brokerageName: Douglas Elliman Real Estate - Park Plaza
description: Built in 2019, 510 Dorchester Ave. is a luxury, 100% owner occupied, 8 unit building that offers everything you are looking for in a South Boston condo. Unparalleled convenience, spectacular views, garage parking and private outdoor space! Unit 4 has direct in-unit elevator access from your deeded garage spot to create a private and elevated city-living experience. Entertain effortlessly in the spacious, open-concept living and dining area, graced with soaring floor-to-ceiling windows that pour in natural light and frame city views. Luxurious touches abound, from rich hardwood flooring and a gas fireplace, to an immersive sound system and top-of-the-line Thermador appliances. Three spacious bedrooms with ample closet space and two full bathrooms create the ideal layout and an in-unit washer/dryer offers the ultimate in convenience. Don’t miss out on this great opportunity for city-living at its finest.
